While loop - It is also a loop used for specific condition in which we do not have idea to how much the iteration will be.
It iterate till the condition is true if the condition is false it break.


Syntax for while loop 

public class Main{
public static void main(String args []){
   int i=0;
   while(i<5){
    System.out.println(i);
    i++;
   }
 }
}
